metadata.name: Shiburai Kabuto #1
metadata.description: The first-generation Kabuto is now live to mint for a limited time! Each first-gen Kabuto has unique utility in coming games, in shared spaces, and across platforms. The Kabuto grants access to an exclusive and protected alpha chat where all can research, share, invest and prosper together and a First-Generation in game shield set in our P2E multiplayer survival game!
